#. type: Plain text
#: ../misc-utils/getopt.1.adoc:56
msgid ""
"Set quoting conventions to those of _shell_. If the *-s* option is not "
"given, the BASH conventions are used. Valid arguments are currently '*sh*' "
"'*bash*', '*csh*', and '*tcsh*'."
