"\"*-e=cpu,node*\" lub \"*--extended=cpu,node*\"."

#. type: Plain text
#: ../sys-utils/lscpu.1.adoc:115
msgid ""
"The default list of columns may be extended if list is specified in the "
"format +list (e.g., lscpu -e=+MHZ)."
